wsdl:operation.name: Update
wsdl:operation.wsdl:documentation:
Summary: Commits a PartDataSet to the database.
Following is information regarding the key structure that make up a PartDataSet.
  • Table Part, Primary Keys: Company, PartNum
    • ;
  • Table PartAttch, Primary Keys: Company, PartNum, DrawingSeq
    • ;
  • Table PartDim, Primary Keys: Company, PartNum, DimCode
    • ;
  • Table PartLangDesc, Primary Keys: Company, PartNum, LangNameID
    • ;
  • Table PartLot, Primary Keys: Company, PartNum, LotNum
    • ;
  • Table PartLotAttch, Primary Keys: Company, PartNum, LotNum, DrawingSeq
    • ;
  • Table PartPlant, Primary Keys: Company, PartNum, Plant
    • ;
  • Table PartWhse, Primary Keys: Company, PartNum, Plant, WarehouseCode
    • ;
  • Table PartBinInfo, Primary Keys: Company, PartNum, Plant, WarehouseCode, BinNum
    • ;
  • Table PartRev, Primary Keys: Company, PartNum, RevisionNum, AltMethod
    • ;
  • Table PartRevAttch, Primary Keys: Company, PartNum, RevisionNum, AltMethod, DrawingSeq
    • ;
  • Table PartAudit, Primary Keys: Company, PartNum, RevisionNum, AltMethod, ChangeDate, ChangeTime
    • ;
  • Table PartSubs, Primary Keys: Company, PartNum, SubPart
